<doc id="1129797" wikidata="Q8038105" url="?curid=1129797" title="Wretched Ones">
<text>The Wretched Ones are an American punk band from Midland Park, New Jersey, United States. They had formerly belonged to The Burnt and The Wretched. Early in the 1990s, their song &quot;Oi! Rodgers&quot; had a modest underground success.

